		bounding box of an element's background.
	</h2>

	<div class='max-h-288 overflow-y-auto mb-32'>
		<table class='vv-table'>
			<thead class='sticky z-sticky top-0 bg-surface'>
				<tr>
					<th>
						Class
					</th>
					<th>
						Properties
					</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody class='align-baseline'>
				<tr>
					<td
						translate='no'
						class='font-mono text-accent whitespace-nowrap'
